   How to stop and start a container
    39  docker ps
   40  docker stop d5ce
   41  docker ps
   42  docker ps -a
   43  docker start d5ce
   44  docker ps
   
   How to delete the container
    52  docker ps -a
   53  docker rm fe0f
   54  docker rm 5f03
   55  clear
   56  docker ps -a
   57  docker rm d5ce
   58  docker rm d5ce --force
   59  docker ps
   60  docker stop a789
   61  docker ps -a
   62  docker rm a7896
   63  history


